OL,3,CAnger as barrister jailed over fatal
OL,4,Ccrash cleared to return to work
OL,6,FThe friend of a pensioner who was
OL,7,Fkilled by a speeding barrister says
OL,8,Fshe is "bitter" that he has been
OL,9,Fcleared to return to work after
OL,10,Fserving a 23-month prison sentence.
OL,12,FHamish Hickey caused 84-year-old
OL,13,FMichael Lupton fatal injuries when he
OL,14,Fcrashed head-on into his car in
OL,15,FAmpleforth, North Yorkshire, in July
OL,16,F2022.
OL,18,FHe initially told police it was not
OL,19,Fhis fault but later admitted causing
OL,20,Fdeath by dangerous driving and was
OL,21,Fjailed in November 2024.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
