OL,3,CAnger as barrister jailed over fatal
OL,4,Ccrash cleared to return to work
OL,6,FHe was released from prison last
OL,7,FAugust to serve the rest of his
OL,8,Fsentence on licence.
OL,10,FThe Bar Standards Board (BSB) has now
OL,11,Fruled that Hickey can return to the
OL,12,Fbar at the end of his sentence in
OL,13,FSeptember.
OL,15,FIt comes as figures obtained by ITV
OL,16,FNews show at least 115 barristers
OL,17,Fcurrently working in England and Wales
OL,18,Fhave criminal convictions.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
