OL,6,F"(Hickey) is going to go back to his
OL,7,F'x' amount-a-year job. Poor Michael
OL,8,Fhasn't got the chance to live his life
OL,9,Fout.''
OL,11,FHickey, who had penalty points for
OL,12,Fspeeding, was driving up a blind
OL,13,Fsummit on Thorpe Lane near Ampleforth,
OL,14,Fand had his two children in the car,
OL,15,Fwhen he caused the fatal crash.
OL,26,@nD@BpmnD@Ipn
