OL,6,FHe initially denied responsibility,
OL,7,Fclaiming Mr Lupton had been driving in
OL,8,Fthe middle of the road. But, according
OL,9,Fto North Yorkshire Police, he changed
OL,10,Fhis statement after investigations by
OL,11,Fa forensic collision expert proved
OL,12,Fotherwise.
OL,14,FIn addition to his prison sentence he
OL,15,Fwas banned from driving for 35 months.
OL,17,FHe was moved to an open prison a month
OL,18,Finto his sentence and has been allowed
OL,19,Fperiods at home on a "home detention
OL,20,Fcurfew".
