OL,6,FMs Langshaw added: ''Had Hamish not
OL,7,Fbeen who he was I do think he would
OL,8,Fhave got longer. (When) you read about
OL,9,Fother people who've been in prison for
OL,10,Fsimilar things, it's very little
OL,11,Ftime.''
OL,13,FIn its ruling on Hickey's return to
OL,14,Fwork, the BSB said he "has always
OL,15,Fadmitted his guilt and his bitter
OL,16,Fremorse is plain".
OL,26,@pD@RpmpD@Wpn
