OL,6,FIt added: "This, whilst it is not a
OL,7,Fcrime of moral wickedness or
OL,8,Fdishonesty, was criminally dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving that cost an innocent man his
OL,10,Flife.''
OL,12,FHickey has appealed against the
OL,13,Fdecision to suspend him from
OL,14,Fpractising until September, when his
OL,15,Fsentence ends.
