OL,6,FIn a statement to ITV News the BSB
OL,7,Fsaid: ''The tribunal found that, where
OL,8,Fa sentence of 23 months' imprisonment
OL,9,Fwas imposed, public confidence would
OL,10,Fbe damaged if Mr Hickey were permitted
OL,11,Fto return to practise before the
OL,12,Fcompletion of his sentence, including
OL,13,Fany period on licence.
OL,15,F"The panel concluded that the
OL,16,Fappropriate sanction was to order a
OL,17,Fsuspension until 30 September 2026.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
