OL,6,FHamish Hickey is not the only lawyer
OL,7,Fcleared by the Bar Standards Board to
OL,8,Freturn to work after committing a
OL,9,Fcrime.
OL,11,FFigures I obtained from a freedom of
OL,12,Finformation request show there are at
OL,13,Fleast 115 barristers currently working
OL,14,Fin courts up and down the country who
OL,15,Fthemselves have convictions for crimes
OL,16,Fwhere the sentence was at least six
OL,17,Fmonths imprisonment.
OL,19,FBarristers guilty of offences which
OL,20,Fcarry a lesser punishment are not
OL,21,Fobliged to report them to the BSB.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
