OL,6,FIt's interesting, because records show
OL,7,Fthe BSB takes a dim view of some
OL,8,Flawyers who have committed seemingly
OL,9,Fminor misdemeanours.
OL,11,FThe BSB is responsible for regulating
OL,12,Fbarristers and legal services
OL,13,Fbusinesses in England and Wales and it
OL,14,Fpublishes findings of tribunal
OL,15,Fhearings.
OL,17,FRecent publications contain some
OL,18,Fnotable examples.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
