OL,6,FThe BSB said that Hamish Hickey did
OL,7,Fnot ask dishonestly.
OL,9,FWhile working on this story I found it
OL,10,Fdifficult to find anyone working in
OL,11,Fthe legal system who was willing to
OL,12,Fdiscuss how these decisions are made.
OL,14,FI approached the Ministry of Justice
OL,15,Fand the Law Society among other
OL,16,Forganisations.
OL,18,FBut for Michael Lupton's friend Angie
OL,19,FLangshaw there is no ambiguity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
